      <bioghist id="aspace_70976c6abb90e70f50d739d90cd219e2">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Lluís (or Luís) Baró Segimón, soldier in the Spanish Civil War and husband of Pilar Val de Baró. Baró Segimón fought with the Republican 27th Division and lived in Morell, Tarragona.</p>  
